09bc1a46301a80e337c641d8c2b34237bd6a2512.query:
UPDATE server
SET last_seen = NOW()
WHERE public_id = $1
RETURNING id;

8be64ec4e9346b50da5077283506eba825a5ca10.query:
INSERT INTO server (public_id, last_seen, ip_address, port)
VALUES ($1, NOW(), $2, $3)
ON CONFLICT (ip_address, port) DO NOTHING
RETURNING id;

fd94f05d67b1bca75fe386b498bc8372002b8aaf.query:
DELETE
FROM server
WHERE ip_address = $1
    AND port = $2
    AND last_seen < NOW() - INTERVAL '5 seconds'
RETURNING id;
